data.description: Come take a look at your new primary home or investment property. First floor includes 2 bedrooms, 1 full bath, living room, dining room and kitchen. Second floor includes 2 bedrooms, 1 full bath, living room, dining room, kitchen and its own washer and dryer!!  Plus there's more: Basement was finished (bonus rooms!!)  Second set of washer and dryer is located in the basement.  Amundsen(Roald) Park and elementary school is walking distance. Metra station is a five minute drive.    Property is owner occupied by the family. No tenants.  1st floor refrigerator and all in unit air conditioners will not stay with the property.    Property is being sold AS IS: Owner is not responsible for any repairs  All rooms sizes and lot are estimates.
